Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.75,0:00:33.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,What's the point of having a stairway \Nwhen no one ever uses it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:37.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you \Nlast came here to the seabed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,problem child of the Great Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:43.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago, Alaira.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:44.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,It sounds like you've been \Nstirring up trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:52.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,I heard about your new apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:56.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Already? Word travels fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.35,0:00:58.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,Does she have the connection you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:01.12,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,The Brimmed Caps?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,No one's used forbidden magic in four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.99,0:01:08.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,She's an important lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:10.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's not about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:15.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,And she hasn't taken her tests, \Nso she's not my official apprentice yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:17.26,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,Oh, she hasn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.26,0:01:19.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's a bad time for it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,Oh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.41,0:01:25.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,At this time of year, the Dadah Range, \Nwhere the test takes place...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:28.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,They'll be at their highest elevation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.33,0:01:30.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dream of putting \Nsomeone through that test now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:33.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It could get them killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:20.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Hey, Agott.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:24.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Are you sure I should do this? \NMaster Qifrey isn't even here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:27.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,{\an8}You'll be doing it alone \Nwhen you take it anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:30.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}B-But I only just got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I passed the test when I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.69,0:03:36.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,We all have to pass it \Nto become apprentices,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:38.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,so you're in the same boat we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:43.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,The first test is "Consent of the Crown."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:47.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You can only take three contraptions \Nand your components.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.75,0:03:51.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You have to reach the summit of the \NDadah Range purely on your own power,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.97,0:03:55.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,and pick the Diadem Herb \Nthat grows there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.04,0:03:58.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,The Guidance Orb that points \Nthe way to your destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:00.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,and the Vapor Bubble for drinking water...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.84,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,That's probably all you can use right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.08,0:04:07.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Go on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.02,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Um... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.58,0:04:16.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Could I have the shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Those shoes are  too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Yours and Master Qifrey's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I saw the soles glow while \Nyou were flying around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:29.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,So I thought... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:33.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,you could lend me a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:37.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,That's too much, right?! \NForget I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:46.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,For you to borrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.91,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,So just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.55,0:04:56.99,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I forgot to mention it, but you \Nonly get to take this test once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:01.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,If you fail, you'll never be allowed \Nto be Master Qifrey's apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,You'll have to leave the atelier, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.14,0:05:16.43,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm suddenly terrified...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.45,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But I've got to give it my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:21.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No turning back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:26.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,How do I use the Guidance Orb, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:40.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Does it want me to go this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:46.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can handle a little mountain-climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:57.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Agott said she passed when she was ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:03.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,If she could do it at ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:10.48,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can... also...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.76,0:06:19.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.64,0:06:22.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.75,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is the Dadah Range?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:42.29,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Guidance Orb is pointing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:44.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's up there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:51.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I didn't realize they'd be floating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The shoes I borrowed from Agott!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Casting Seal is split between \Nthe right and left foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:33.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Make sure they're perfectly aligned...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:44.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Wow! I'm really floating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:55.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Master Qifrey was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:57.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm like a newborn foal stumbling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:02.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I flew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.68,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Flying can take me to \Nthe summit in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:16.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:18.56,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:26.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll get used to it and be \Nrunning around freely in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:32.08,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Get used to it. Get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:57.69,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Here's the application. \NPlease process it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:58.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch A,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch A,0,0,0,,Thotrey. Number 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,If you'd live in the Great Hall, you wouldn't have to travel so far for every little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.65,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's see... number 12, number 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.61,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,You could bring your apprentices, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't see the box, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:10.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,The Great Hall is \Nthe witches' stronghold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.76,0:09:12.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch A,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's one in the back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,It has everything we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:16.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Which is why I come here \Nwhen I need things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}There it is! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.62,0:09:22.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sir, is this for that Outsider—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:22.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,Your hatred of the Great Hall runs deep, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:23.21,GJM_Main_1080p,Witch A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thotrey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.21,0:09:24.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Thotrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:26.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on those apprentices of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:31.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Alaira,0,0,0,,You never know what children that age \Nmight get up to without adults around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.14,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I think I'm keeping my balance \Nbetter than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Maybe now I can go a little higher...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:27.13,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,A brushbuddy! I've never seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.67,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The shoes are caked with mud...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Casting Seal came off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.31,0:10:57.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No way! Because I wiped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:10:59.50,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Oh, no! Oh, no! Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:01.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I know! I'll just draw it back on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:07.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Conjuring Ink spilled in my bag...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:14.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:18.71,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Is it all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:21.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Hey, Agott. Have you seen Coco?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:26.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,It's about time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.96,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Coco's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:31.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,She went to the Dadah Range for her test.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,What?! By herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.09,0:11:35.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,But she just got to the atelier!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:36.59,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,C'mon, Agott!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:40.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Most people take the test \Nbefore coming here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.39,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:49.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,If she can't pass a test that simple, \Nshe shouldn't be an apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:55.33,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I hate people who can't do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:57.74,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I gain no benefit being around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.26,0:12:01.24,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially{\i0} Outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.11,0:12:06.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,Don't worry. She'll fail and \Ncome back soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:11.78,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,The Dadah Range is at its \Nhighest this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:15.80,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,She won't be able to fly that high \Nwith just my Sylph Shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:19.01,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,She doesn't even know the rules \Nor realize how dangerous this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:24.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Agott,0,0,0,,I don't want someone \Nlike that in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Tetia, are you not going to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.52,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I am, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I feel kinda... down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:43.06,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,Going for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.41,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Am I seriously the only one who's worried?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:50.42,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do but wait \Nfor Master Qifrey regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.80,0:13:01.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.28,0:13:05.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I tried drawing it back on \Nwith what little ink I had left,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:07.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,but I can't even float now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:11.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The ink soaks in and dilutes because it's still wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:22.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,If I drew it directly on the soles of my feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,No! Magic drawn onto the body is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:43.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I don't know what kind of magic \NI should use at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.72,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I guess Agott was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:08.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Anyone can draw a spell, but that \Ndoesn't mean they'll be good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:13.66,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I guess you have to be a special \Nkind of person to be a witch after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:26.17,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,They've all been drawing spells \Nsince they were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's not something I could ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco's Mother,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nice and straight. {booooo}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:10.22,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had no idea this village had \Nsuch a skilled craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:13.60,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is real magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:19.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I have it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.53,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I have my own magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:51.93,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,If I let a little water \Nsoak in and dilute it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:16:00.31,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The mud's dried on my wet cape \Nand made it a little stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:02.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I think I can draw on it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:32.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's natural to have unsteady hands \Nwhen you're learning to use a new tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:39.85,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I'll swap it for a tool I'm used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.86,0:16:44.73,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}My fingers begin to dance of their own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.01,0:16:47.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:56.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Morning, brushbuddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.88,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You've made yourself at home, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.87,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's a pretty ugly Casting Seal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.20,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,To draw one properly, \Nthe sigil needs to be centered,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:09.63,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,and the signs are supposed to be uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,He taught me that if the signs aren't balanced,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:14.64,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,it can put too much energy \Ninto one direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:17.89,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I wanted to see what would happen \Nif I made one long on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:21.10,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if it'll work, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:30.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,You want to come, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Really? Hold on tight, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:37.49,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm closing the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:47.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,What? What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Did I get the sign's direction wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:26.00,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.25,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm flying with my own spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.79,0:18:31.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,A real cloak of flight...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:33.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:52.09,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I never thought helping Mom \Nwould help me learn magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:56.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,But the Diadem Herb is higher than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.47,0:19:12.55,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,The Diadem Herb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.15,0:20:13.44,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:22.37,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait for me, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:27.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll take responsibility for what I've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.46,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,So Coco went to the Dadah Range \Nto take the test for herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:40.30,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,That's too dangerous! \NI have to go save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.47,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,But she'll fail if you interrupt her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:44.97,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It was too soon for her to take the test anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:49.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,She hasn't been living around magic \Nher whole life like we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,If anything were to happen to Coco...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.69,0:20:55.11,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\i1}She wouldn't be the only loss suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:55.86,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:03.40,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:05.34,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey/Tetia,0,0,0,,Coco!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.23,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:09.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,Coco! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:13.16,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,I was so totally, totally worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:15.92,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Agott!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:19.76,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I got the "Consent of the Crown."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:25.36,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,This is the proof I need, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:36.62,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Coco.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.62,0:21:39.82,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's extremely dangerous to cast spells
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:43.28,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,without the proper preparation \Nand fundamental knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:45.15,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,I thought you'd learned that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:50.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You could easily have died back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:52.79,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Never do anything like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.32,0:21:56.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Master Qifrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:02.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Besides, you didn't need to put yourself \Nin danger to prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.05,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,You're already my apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.09,0:22:20.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.83,0:22:27.27,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The proof that you're a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.88,0:22:29.58,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,It's both our pride
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.98,0:22:34.51,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,and a shackle that rests atop our head \Nso we don't abuse our magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:48.81,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,As long as you wear it, \Ndon't forget its weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:54.03,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,The pointed cap is watching your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.48,0:22:58.07,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.37,0:23:00.57,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:04.04,GJM_Main_1080p,Qifrey,0,0,0,,{\an8}All right. Let's go back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:04.90,GJM_Main_1080p,Coco,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.35,GJM_Main_1080p,Tetia,0,0,0,,{\an8}Guess we'd better eat first!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:13.98,GJM_Main_1080p,Richeh,0,0,0,,{\an8}Take a bath, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.44,0:23:34.38,GJM_Main_1080p,Iguin,0,0,0,,The seed has sprouted.
